HEADWORD: Sigla
<hw>Sig"la</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n. pl.</pos> <ety>[L.]</ety>
<def>The signs, abbreviations, letters, or characters standing for
words, shorthand, etc., in ancient manuscripts, or on coins, medals,
etc.</def> <rj><au>W. Savage.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

